trans_text: It's too small for the price of the tangsuyuk filling ㅠㅠ?????. I'm looking forward to the review of Galbi Jjamppong. I don't like the taste because it's too small. Tray jajangmyeon. text: 군만두랑 옛날볶음밥 맛있어요~ 갈비짬뽕은 맛이 없는건 아닌데 가격대비 평범한 맛이에요..면이 맛없어서 밥이랑 먹는게 딱이에요.
trans_text: Fried dumplings and old fried rice are good Galbi jjamppong is not bad, but it tastes normal for its price..It's perfect to eat it with rice because the noodles are not good.
It's not cheap, but it's really good

text: 짬뽕은 야채와 해물 불맛 좋고 짜장면은 순한맛입니다 탕수육은 가격대비 양이 적어요 전체적으로 맛과양에비하면 비쌉니다ㅜㅜ
trans_text: Spicy seafood and vegetables are good, and black bean noodles are mild Tangsuyuk is not expensive compared to the price. Overall, it's expensive compared to the taste and amountㅜㅜ

text:

trans_text: It's too salty and the price is very expensive compared to the taste.. 7,000 won is enough taste.. It's too salty...

text: 가격이 비싸서 걱정했는데 양이 푸짐하고 맛있어요~

text: 지인짜 맛있어요 얼큰하고 해물도 많고 먼도 수타로 뽑아서 8천원 이란 금액이 아깝지 않아요
trans_text: It's delicious. It's spicy and has a lot of seafood. It's not a waste of 8,000 won
